OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1778764275
OL,3,CPrison bosses face reprimand after
OL,4,Cexposing staff and inmates to radon
OL,6,FThe prison and probation service is
OL,7,Ffacing a reprimand after inmates and
OL,8,Fstaff at HMP Dartmoor were exposed to
OL,9,Fdangerous levels of radioactive radon
OL,10,Fgas.
OL,12,FA report from the Health and Safety
OL,13,FExecutive said levels were
OL,14,F"significantly above the legal limit"
OL,15,Fand "for a prolonged period of time".
OL,17,FThe national regulator of workplace
OL,18,Fhealth and safety confirmed it will
OL,19,Fissue a Crown Censure to His Majesty's
OL,20,FPrison and Probation Service (HMPSS).
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
