OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1778764275
OL,3,CPrison bosses face reprimand after
OL,4,Cexposing staff and inmates to radon
OL,6,FA Crown Censure is the process by
OL,7,Fwhich the regulator holds Crown bodies
OL,8,Fto account for serious breaches of
OL,9,Fhealth and safety law.
OL,11,FThe HSE says it was informed by HMPSS
OL,12,Fabout the suspected overexposure to
OL,13,Fradon in February 2023.
OL,15,FHMP Dartmoor closed in August 2024
OL,16,Fafter abnormal levels of radioactive
OL,17,Fradon gas had been detected at the
OL,18,FDevon jail.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
