PN,43503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1778764275
OL,3,CPrison bosses face reprimand after
OL,4,Cexposing staff and inmates to radon
OL,6,FA statement from the regulator said:
OL,7,F"HSE took enforcement action
OL,8,Fhighlighting breaches of the
OL,9,Fregulations in both February and in
OL,10,FDecember 2023. HMPPS decided to
OL,11,Fmothball HMP Dartmoor in 2024.
OL,13,F"Following an investigation by HSE
OL,14,Finspectors, a file was passed to HSE's
OL,15,Flegal services division for review,
OL,16,Fwhich in accordance with Code for
OL,17,FCrown Prosecutors has authorised a
OL,18,FCrown Censure.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1778764275
OL,3,CPrison bosses face reprimand after
OL,4,Cexposing staff and inmates to radon
OL,6,F"A Crown Censure is the maximum
OL,7,Fsanction available to HSE against a
OL,8,FCrown body.
OL,10,F"A decision to authorise a Crown
OL,11,FCensure is not a formal finding of
OL,12,Fguilt - is equivalent to a decision to
OL,13,Fauthorise criminal charges, in line
OL,14,Fwith the Code for Crown Prosecutors.
OL,16,F"Following the decision to issue a
OL,17,FCrown Censure, a formal hearing will
OL,18,Ftake place to confirm the censure.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
